 gap-2.5 px-4 py-2.5 text-start focus-visible:outline-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 md:px-6\" data-toc-popover-trigger=\"\"><svg role=\"progressbar\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-valuenow=\"0\" aria-valuemin=\"0\" aria-valuemax=\"1\" class=\"shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" class=\"stroke-current/25\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-dasharray=\"69.11503837897544\" stroke-dashoffset=\"69.11503837897544\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" transform=\"rotate(-90 12 12)\" class=\"transition-all\"></circle></svg><span class=\"grid flex-1 *:my-auto *:row-start-1 *:col-start-1\"><span class=\"truncate transition-[opacity,translate,color]\">Sales Hub</span><span class=\"truncate transition-[opacity,translate] opacity-0 translate-y-full pointer-events-none\"></span></span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down shrink-0 transition-transform mx-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div data-state=\"closed\" id=\"radix-_R_1av5u9flb_\" hidden=\"\" data-toc-popover-content=\"\" class=\"overflow-hidden\"></div></header></div><article id=\"nd-page\" data-full=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col w-full max-w-[900px] mx-auto [grid-area:main] px-4 py-6 gap-4 md:px-6 md:pt-8 xl:px-8 xl:pt-14 xl:layout:[--fd-toc-width:268px]\"><h1 class=\"text-[1.75em] font-semibold\">Sales Hub</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-fd-muted-foreground mb-0\">View, filter, and export your full sales history — appointments, payments, memberships, vouchers, products, and tips</p><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-2 items-center border-b pb-6\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-3.5 [&amp;_svg]:text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy Markdown</button><button type=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_9qav5u9flb_\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 data-[state=open]:bg-fd-accent data-[state=open]:text-fd-accent-foreground\">Open<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down size-3.5 text-fd-muted-foreground\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"prose flex-1\"><p>The Sales Hub is your complete record of everything that&#x27;s been sold or paid for. Click <strong>Sales</strong> in the left menu and you&#x27;ll see a sidebar with eight sections. Each one is focused on a different part of your business and has its own search, date filter, and <strong>Export</strong> button.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"daily-sales\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#daily-sales\" class=\"peer\">Daily Sales</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p><strong>Sales → Daily Sales</strong></p>\n<p>Your end-of-day summary. Use the <strong>Today</strong>, <strong>&lt;</strong>, and <strong>&gt;</strong> buttons to pick any day and see a full breakdown of what happened.</p>\n<p>The page is split into three parts:</p>\n<p><strong>Transaction summary</strong>\nA table showing what was sold by item type (e.g., Service, Product), how many were sold, and the net total.</p>\n<p><strong>Cash movement summary</strong>\nA breakdown of how payments were collected — showing each payment method (Cash, Online, Card, etc.) and the amount collected through each. Also shows the total <strong>Payments collected</strong> and how much of that was <strong>tips</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Summary bar</strong>\nFour quick-view numbers at the bottom:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Total Sales</strong> — total revenue for the day</li>\n<li><strong>Total Transactions</strong> — number of completed transactions</li>\n<li><strong>Sale Types</strong> — how many different item types were sold</li>\n<li><strong>Payment Methods</strong> — how many different payment methods were used</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"appointments\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#appointments\" class=\"peer\">Appointments</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p><strong>Sales → Appointments</strong></p>\n<p>A full list of every appointment-based sale. Use this when you need to look up a specific service, client visit, or check what was charged and whether a discount was applied.</p>\n<p><strong>Columns:</strong> Sale ID · Client (name + phone) · Service · Sale Date · Team Member · Unit Price · Quantity · Discount · Total Price</p>\n<p>Discounts show in red when applied. Search by client name or service, or filter by date range. Click <strong>Export</strong> to download as CSV.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"sales-transactions\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#sales-transactions\" class=\"peer\">Sales Transactions</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p><strong>Sales → Sales</strong></p>\n<p>Your complete transaction history across all sale types. By default it shows the last 30 days.</p>\n<p><strong>Columns:</strong> Sale ID · Payment Date · Client · Team Members · Payment Method · Tips · Status · Amount</p>\n<p>The <strong>Status</strong> column shows either:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Completed</strong> — the sale went through successfully</li>\n<li><strong>Voided</strong> (red badge) — the sale was reversed after the fact</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Click any <strong>Sale ID</strong> to open the full <a href=\"#sale-details\">Sale Details panel</a>.</p>\n<p>Click any <strong>Client name</strong> to open their <a href=\"#client-profile\">Client Profile</a>.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"payments\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#payments\" class=\"peer\">Payments</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p><strong>Sales → Payments</strong></p>\n<p>Every payment transaction that was successfully collected — similar to Sales Transactions but focused on the payment side only. Voided sales are excluded here.</p>\n<p><strong>Columns:</strong> Sale ID · Payment Date · Client · Team Members · Payment Method · Tips · Status · Amount</p>\n<p>Tips show in the Tips column when they were added to the sale. Search by client name or sale ID, or filter by date range.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"memberships\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#memberships\" class=\"peer\">Memberships</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p><strong>Sales → Memberships</strong></p>\n<p>All membership packages that have been sold, with live session tracking.</p>\n<p><strong>Columns:</strong> Purchase Date · Client · Membership name · Service · Sessions (used / remaining with a progress bar) · Cost · Status</p>\n<p>The <strong>Status</strong> shows either <strong>Active</strong> (sessions still available) or <strong>Completed</strong> (all sessions used). The progress bar makes it easy to see at a glance how far through a package a client is.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"vouchers\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#vouchers\" class=\"peer\">Vouchers</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p><strong>Sales → Vouchers</strong></p>\n<p>All vouchers that have been purchased or redeemed. Search by client name, voucher name, or voucher code. Filter by date range to narrow results.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"products\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#products\" class=\"peer\">Products</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p><strong>Sales → Products</strong></p>\n<p>A record of every product sold, with live stock levels.</p>\n<p><strong>Columns:</strong> Sale ID · Product Name · Category · Brand · Quantity · Unit Price · Total Price · Current Stock · Sale Date · Status</p>\n<p>The <strong>Current Stock</strong> column shows a warning icon (⚠) when stock is running low. The <strong>Status</strong> badge will show <strong>Low Stock</strong> to flag items that need reordering.</p>\n<p>Search by product name, SKU, barcode, or category.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"tips\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#tips\" class=\"peer\">Tips</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p><strong>Sales → Tips</strong></p>\n<p>Every tip that&#x27;s been collected, attributed to the staff member who received it.</p>\n<p><strong>Columns:</strong> Sale ID · Tip Amount · Staff Member · Payment Method · Sale Total · Date</p>\n<p>Search by staff name, payment method, or sale ID. Filter by date range.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"client-profile\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#client-profile\" class=\"peer\">Client Profile</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Anywhere you see a <strong>client name</strong> shown as a blue link (in Sales Transactions, Payments, etc.), you can click it to open that client&#x27;s full profile in a panel on the right.</p>\n<p>The profile is split into two parts:</p>\n<p><strong>Left — Client details</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Name, phone, and email</li>\n<li><strong>Edit client</strong> — update their contact details</li>\n<li><strong>Add review</strong> — add an internal note or review about the client</li>\n<li>Date of birth (optional)</li>\n<li>Date the client was created in the system</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Middle — Navigation tabs</strong>\nSwitch between different views of the client&#x27;s history:</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Tab</th><th>What it shows</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Appointments</td><td>All appointments with status badges (Paid, Scheduled, No Show)</td></tr><tr><td>Sales</td><td>All completed sales with service, total, and a View Details button</td></tr><tr><td>Products</td><td>Products purchased by this client</td></tr><tr><td>Vouchers</td><td>Vouchers associated with this client</td></tr><tr><td>Memberships</td><td>Active and completed membership packages (shows count badge)</td></tr><tr><td>Loyalty</td><td>Loyalty programme activity</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p><strong>Right — Detail view</strong>\nClicking any item in the tabs shows the full detail on the right side. For example, clicking a sale shows the service, time, staff, subtotal, VAT, and total.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"sale-details\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#sale-details\" class=\"peer\">Sale Details</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Clicking a <strong>Sale ID</strong> or <strong>View Details</strong> anywhere in the Sales Hub opens the full Sale Details panel. This shows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Status badge</strong> (e.g., Completed)</li>\n<li>Client name and phone</li>\n<li><strong>VAT Invoice</strong> number and date</li>\n<li>Services performed with time, duration, and assigned team</li>\n<li><strong>Staff Information</strong> — assigned staff member and receptionist</li>\n<li>Subtotal, VAT (5%), and Total</li>\n<li><strong>Print icons</strong> — print as thermal receipt or standard A4 invoice</li>\n<li><strong>Sale-ID</strong> (copyable)</li>\n<li><strong>Void Sale</strong> button — reverses the transaction if an error was made</li>\n<li><strong>Back to Appointment</strong> button — returns to the linked appointment</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-warning, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>Voiding a sale cannot be undone. Only use this if there was a genuine error with the transaction.</p></div></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"quick-reference\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#quick-reference\" class=\"peer\">Quick reference</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Section</th><th>Best used for</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Daily Sales</td><td>End-of-day reconciliation — cash, card, and tips totals</td></tr><tr><td>Appointments</td><td>Looking up a specific service or client visit</td></tr><tr><td>Sales Transactions</td><td>Full transaction log including voided sales</td></tr><tr><td>Payments</td><td>Collected payments only, with tips</td></tr><tr><td>Memberships</td><td>Session usage and package status</td></tr><tr><td>Vouchers</td><td>Gift card purchases and redemptions</td></tr><tr><td>Products</td><td>Retail sales with live stock levels</td></tr><tr><td>Tips</td><td>Gratuity records by staff member</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"@container grid gap-4 grid-cols-2\"><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full\" href=\"/docs/checkout\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-left -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg><p>Checkout</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">Collect payment, print receipts, and manage completed sales</p></a><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full text-end\" href=\"/docs/catalog\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium flex-row-reverse\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><p>Catalog &amp; Inventory</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">Set up your services, products, memberships, vouchers, and manage stock</p></a></div></article><div id=\"nd-toc\" class=\"sticky top-(--fd-docs-row-1) h-[calc(var(--fd-docs-height)-var(--fd-docs-row-1))] flex flex-col [grid-area:toc] w-(--fd-toc-width) pt-12 pe-4 pb-2 max-xl:hidden\"><h3 id=\"toc-title\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-text-align-start size-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 5H3\"></path><path d=\"M15 12H3\"></path><pa